ear ago</div><div class="wp-facebook-feedback"><span class="wp-facebook-stars"></span><span class="wp-facebook-text">第一次包車從台北到花蓮，窗口聯繫回應超迅速，安排的司機李大哥人也很nice，雖然一路塞塞塞，但是還是有玩到景點，很棒的經驗！</span></div></div></div><div class="wp-facebook-review"><div class="wp-facebook-left"><img src="https://skytour.tw/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/000193.jpg" class="rplg-review-avatar" alt="呂嘉銘" width="50" height="50" title="呂嘉銘"></div><div class="wp-facebook-right"><a href="https://facebook.com/3672206519460185" class="wp-facebook-name" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">呂嘉銘</a><div class="wp-facebook-time" data-time="2020-06-25T02:51:27+0000">a year ago</div><div class="wp-facebook-feedback"><span class="wp-facebook-stars"></span><span class="wp-facebook-text">這是我第一次包車-------從開始聯絡就決定是你們了！完全不需要去比價，在我的心裡~服務比價格更重要呀！完全感受到那份熱情、真誠，真的超級謝謝你們呀！</span></div></div></div><div class="wp-facebook-review"><div class="wp-facebook-left"><img src="https://skytour.tw/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/000194.jpg" class="rplg-review-avatar" alt="Michelle Lin" width="50" height="50" title="Michelle Lin"></div><div class="wp-facebook-right"><a href="https://facebook.com/10156914217421595" class="wp-facebook-name" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Michelle Lin</a><div class="wp-facebook-time" data-time="2020-06-24T14:21:56+0000">a year ago</div><div class="wp-facebook-feedback"><span class="wp-facebook-stars"></span><span class="wp-facebook-text">大推光哥，熱情專業、開車穩、車子很乾淨。再推客服小姐很有耐心解釋，成就我們美好的回憶👍</span></div></div></div><div class="wp-facebook-review"><div class="wp-facebook-left"><img src="https://skytour.tw/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/000195.jpg" class="rplg-review-avatar" alt="潘婷" width="50" height="50" title="潘婷"></div><div class="wp-facebook-right"><a href="https://facebook.com/3053616238054353" class="wp-facebook-name" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">潘婷</a><div class="wp-facebook-time" data-time="2020-06-24T04:31:03+0000">a year ago</div><div class="wp-facebook-feedback"><span class="wp-facebook-stars"></