lass="wp-facebook-right"><a href="https://facebook.com/10211936765849290" class="wp-facebook-name" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Lena Lin</a><div class="wp-facebook-time" data-time="2019-07-12T17:06:52+0000">3 years ago</div><div class="wp-facebook-feedback"><span class="wp-facebook-stars"></span><span class="wp-facebook-text">滿推薦大玩家的包車，服務很好，也會推薦不錯的行程，司機楊先生服務很好，很親切，也很健談，讓我們一天下來覺得對台東又更深一層的認識與喜歡。下次有機會一定會跟親友推薦大玩家包車。謝謝你們😊</span></div></div></div><div class="wp-facebook-review"><div class="wp-facebook-left"><img src="https://skytour.tw/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/000398.jpg" class="rplg-review-avatar" alt="陳佳蕙" width="50" height="50" title="陳佳蕙"></div><div class="wp-facebook-right"><a href="https://facebook.com/2547077888670842" class="wp-facebook-name" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">陳佳蕙</a><div class="wp-facebook-time" data-time="2019-07-10T01:21:14+0000">3 years ago</div><div class="wp-facebook-feedback"><span class="wp-facebook-stars"></span><span class="wp-facebook-text">7/7-7/8這兩天和家人一起包車從台北到南投出遊，這麼多包車出遊的經驗，這次讓我感到特別不一樣，我們的司機是為女性，她非常的親切跟熱情接待，讓我印象深刻的是其中有一天我們到7-11買東西，突然下起大雨，她迅速的把車移到我們淋不到雨的地方<span>... </span><span class="wp-more">讓我們上車，如此貼心的舉動讓我們非常感動。謝謝大玩家為我們安排的司機，價格也非常的親民，未來的每趟旅遊，都會再找大玩家👍🏻👍🏻</span><span class="wp-more-toggle">read more</span></span></div></div></div><div class="wp-facebook-review"><div class="wp-facebook-left"><img src="https://skytour.tw/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/000399.jpg" class="rplg-review-avatar" alt="Tsung-hsi Fu" width="50" height="50" title="Tsung-hsi Fu"></div><div class="wp-facebook-right"><a href="https://facebook.com/2849643651729342" class="wp-facebook-name" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Tsung-hsi Fu</a><div class="wp-facebook-time" data-time="2019-07-08T07:45:46+0000">3 years ago</div><div class="wp-facebook-feedback"><span class="wp-facebook-stars"></span><span class="wp-facebook-text">客服回應快，司機態度佳，很值得推薦！</span></div></div></div><div class="wp-facebook-review"><div class="wp-facebook-left"><img src="https://skytour.tw/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/000400.jpg" class="rplg-review-avatar" alt="Jerry Li" width="50" height="50" title="Jerry Li"></div><div class="wp-facebook-right"><a href="https://facebook.com/2561873630497838" class="wp-facebook-name" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Jerry Li</a><div class="wp-facebook-time" data-time="2019-07-03T14:57:39+0000">3 years ago</div><div class="wp-facebook-feedback"><span class="wp-facebook-stars"></span><span class="wp-facebook-text">司机服务热情，细致到位，主动给我们提供各种路线和游玩地点供选择，甚至还请我们吃东西，车上每天都会准备纸巾和矿泉水，给我们的台湾之行留下了非常好的印象。包车租赁首选！</span></div></div></div><div class="wp-facebook-review"><div class="wp-facebook-left"><img src="https://skytour.tw/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/000401.jpg" class="rplg-review-avatar" alt="林素玉" width="50" height="50" title="林素玉"></div><div class="wp-facebook-right"><a href="https://facebook.com/477510442995794" class="wp-facebook-name" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">林素玉</a><div class="wp-facebook-time" data-time="2019-06-27T10:40:52+0000">3 years ago</div><div class="wp-facebook-feedback"><span class="wp-facebook-stars"></span><span class="wp-facebook-text">真的很感謝大玩家包車旅遊的幫忙，雖然我們要求很多，但還是很耐心的一一幫我們處理，司機大哥也真的很親切，讓長輩都玩得很開心,真的很推薦大玩家包車旅遊！</span></div></div></div><div class="wp-facebook-review"><div class="wp-facebook-left"><img src="https://skytour.tw/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/000402.jpg" class="rplg-review-avatar" alt="葉燕珍" width="50" height="50" title="葉燕珍"></div><div class="wp-facebook-right"><a href="https://facebook.com/1190248591158389" class="wp-facebook-name" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">葉燕珍</a><div class="wp-facebook-time" data-time="2019-06-22T06:57:06+0000">3 years ago</div><div class="wp-facebook-feedback"><span class="wp-facebook-stars"></span><span class="wp-facebook-text">我們是台東旅遊，導遊司機黃先生講話很風趣，車上也很乾淨，安排的行程也很好，長輩很滿意，照相超美，很推👍</span></div></div></div><div class="wp-facebook-review"><div class="wp-facebook-left"><img src="https://skytour.tw/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/000403.jpg" class="rplg-review-avatar" alt="Eden Wang" width="50" height="50" title="Eden Wang"></div><div class="wp-facebook-right"><a href="https://facebook.com/2473401479549737" class="wp-facebook-name" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Eden Wang</a><div class="wp-facebook-time" data-time="2019-06-21T14:09:36+0000">3 years ago</div><div class="wp-facebook-feedback"><span class="wp-facebook-stars"></span><span class="wp-facebook-text">車廂舒服乾淨，司機師傅親切，讚👍</span></div></div></div><div class="wp-facebook-review"><div class="wp-facebook-left"><img src="https://skytour.tw/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/000404.jpg" class="rplg-review-avatar" alt="Liz Cyt" width="50" height="50" title="Liz Cyt"></div><div class="wp-facebook-right"><a href="https://facebook.com/140120133742247" class="wp-facebook-name" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Liz Cyt</a><div class="wp-facebook-time" data-time="2019-06-21T13:56:17+0000">3 years ago</div><div class="wp-facebook-feedback"><span class="wp-facebook-stars"></span><span class="wp-facebook-text">司機親切有禮！非常推薦～～</span></div></div></div><div class="wp-facebook-review"><div class="wp-facebook-left"><img src="https://skytour.tw/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/000405.jpg" class="rplg-review-avatar" alt="Vita Lin" width="50" height="50" title="Vita Lin"></div><div class="wp-facebook-right"><a href="https://facebook.com/1738594196243613" class="wp-facebook-name" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Vita Lin</a><div class="wp-facebook-time" data-time="2019-06-09T05:55:20+0000">3 years ago</div><div class="wp-facebook-feedback"><span class="wp-facebook-stars"></span><span class="wp-facebook-text">客服很有耐心 服務很好司機人也很好 很熱心的講解</span></div></div></div><div class="wp-facebook-review"><div class="wp-facebook-left"><img src="https://skytour.tw/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/000406.jpg" class="rplg-review-avatar" alt="BonBon Su" width="50" height="50" title="BonBon Su"></div><div class="wp-facebook-right"><a href="https://facebook.com/10219251759867458" class="wp-facebook-name" target=